				<td colspan="2"><span>PoI is great xp, expecially at 52. The only problem you might run into is the fact that they resist, alot, especially on the bard slows at your level. You might also have fun finding out that some are not lullable, and I do not remember thier names, but despite that PoI is great xp if you can get a coherent group together. I see a lot of clerics die due to lack of aggro control in PoI, mostly on the archaics if your tank is not solid. Overall, a great place to group, if you can convince your group to move to the ramp or deeper, you might find it less crowded, as the entrance always has at least 3 groups fighting over 20 feet of space (at least on AyRo). 
<br />
I did try swarming here once but it was around 4:00 in the morning and I don't remember much except the cr a few hours later. 
<br />
Don't drink and swarm
<br />

