				<td colspan="2"><span>If you want some excitement (and this is off-topic a bit) it is a little-known fact that Nitram Anizok who lives in the gnome hut partway into POI is a merchant who sells a couple of Tinkering items that you can ONLY get off him.  That means taking a group and clearing to him so you can buy supplies, which is a major pain in the butt for most people.  But a bard can get items from him with little difficulty.  Just fire up Selo's and run there, fading as you hit the steps to his house.  Buy what you need, then run back and fade just before you train the folks XPing at zone in.  Almost as much fun as confirming the Zeks or Shei Vinitras visually.  <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-11.gif" border="0" alt="Cool" hspace="2" /></span></td>
